text: On þisre worulde fruman god ælmihtig gesceop and geworhte on syx dagum ealle gesceafta, and ðæs seofoþan dæges he gereste hine.
And on syx ylda is þeos woruld eac todæled, and seo seofoðe belimpð to þære ecan reste.

An yld is geteald of Adame to Noe, oþer of Noe to Abrahame, ðridde of Abrahame to Dauide, feorðe of Dauide to ðam myclan heregange, fifte of ðam heregange to Cristes gebyrdtiman, sixte of ures drihtnes gebyrdtide to þam ende, þe god ana wat, seofoðe belimpð to þam toweardan life.
